headlines.description: — Jonas Valanciunas scored a season-high 29 points and matched his season best with 20 rebounds to lead the Memphis Grizzlies to a 127-112 victory over the Washington Wizards on Wednesday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Valanciunas scores 29, leads Grizzlies over Wizards 127-112

events.name: San Antonio Spurs at Dallas Mavericks

headlines.description: — Luka Doncic had 22 points, 12 rebounds and 12 assists in his 33rd triple-double, Kristaps Porzingis had 28 points and 14 rebounds and the Dallas Mavericks used a late run to pull away and beat the San Antonio Spurs 115-104 on Wednesday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Mavericks pull away late to beat Spurs 115-104
